{
  "id": "adv_main_02_03_04",
  "title": "東京編1章14話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "（合宿初日の夜）\n（私達はリビングで寝ることにした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The first night of the bootcamp‚）\n（we all decide to sleep in the living room.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 7.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "五人で一緒に寝るなんて初めてだね\nなんだか修学旅行みたいでワクワクするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the first time we’ve all slept in the same room.\nThis kind of feels like a school trip. I’m really excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから布団に入って怖い話でもする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Want to get in our futons and tell ghost stories?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "そこは……恋バナがお約束では……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… the standard move here would be boy-talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.00000004768372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "恋バナ……今夜は興奮して眠れないかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Boy-talk? I might get too excited to sleep tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.50000004768372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……私はさっき観たホラー映画のせいで\n眠れないかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of the horror movie we just watched‚\nI might not be able to sleep either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.654678062292252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……まさかサニピのみんなと\n同じ部屋で寝られるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… look at me‚ with Sunny Peace‚\nsleeping in the same room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.53333319028218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　落ち着け私！！\n私、外に出て頭を冷やしてきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Stay calm‚ Satomi.\nEr‚ I’m going to go outside to cool my head!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.16666652361551,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666809717824,
          "startTime": 44.13333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "……さとみちゃん、どうしちゃったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s going on with Satomi-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.15402274022156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルオタクとマネージャー……\n二律背反……葛藤……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s a fangirl and a manager…\nThe two sides fight… and there’s chaos.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.15275281160725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……あははっ！\nさとみさんって面白い人だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha!\nSatomi-san sure is a funny person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3181373903121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.492378933128265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　良かったって何が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What are you relieved about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.292378933128255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ううん、なんでもないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it’s nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.96446517198934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あら、隠しごとなんて水くさいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C’mon‚ don’t hide it from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.67661932199849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "今は夜の女子会……\n思ったことは、全部言っていい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re having girl-talk right now.\nSay everything that’s on your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.48682347823834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "あの……\nみんなが変わっていないことが嬉しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um…\n…really happy that nobody has changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.953490144905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 81.453490144905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "最近は一緒にいる時間が減って\nみんなと距離が出来たように感じていたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been spending less time together lately‚\nand I felt like we were drifting apart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5201568115717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。また昔みたいに話が出来て……\nみんな全然変わってなくて、ちょっと安心したかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Talking again like old times‚\nI’ve realized nobody’s changed at all. I’m kind of relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5201568115717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんも不安を感じてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were scared too‚ Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.58682347823836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "だって、みんなどんどん仕事が増えて\nアイドルとして成長してて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah. Everyone started getting more work‚\nand growing on their own as idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.75745841552484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ取り残されてるような気がして……\n不安にもなるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt like I was the only one getting left behind.\nOf course I got scared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.25745841552484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに置いていかれないようにもっと頑張らなきゃ\n成長しなきゃって……ちょっと焦ってたかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I had to work harder so I wouldn’t get left behind.\nI had to grow faster… and it was stressing me out a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.79079174885824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "このままみんなの心がバラバラになるんじゃないかって\n私も心配だったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also thought we were all drifting apart‚\nand it worried me‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.79706004696584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.20658382924182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "私も……怜ちゃんと、喧嘩みたいになって……\nどうしたらいいのか……分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too… when you and I started fighting‚ Rei-chan‚\nI wasn’t sure what I should do about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.23601693661809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "私も、不安だったんだ……\nみんなと一緒にいられなくて、ずっと不安だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was scared‚ too.\nI was so scared to be away from you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1026836032849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "なんとかしなきゃって……\n一人で悩んで、焦ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I had to do something to fix it.\nI kept my worries to myself‚ and it stressed me out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.83601693661825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも同じだったんだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I guess we all felt the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.23601693661826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……泣いてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… are you crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4026836032847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
